standard as marryModule and ModuleSync); Gen2 Yazaki stays ungated (bench-
verified). KeyProgTab surfaces an opt-in checkbox when the patcher reports the
UNVERIFIED block. Charger62BenchPanel is Gen2-EEE-specific so the gate never
fires there. CI test covers refuse / acknowledge / Gen2-ungated. esbuild-valid.
